  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"content\"\u003e\n\n\u003carticle\u003e\n\n\t\n \t\n \t\n\n \t\n\n \t\n\t\t\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eThis berry arugula salad is perfect for the summer! Topped with honey pistachio clusters and goat cheese vinaigrette, it’s simple, delicious, satisfying an super festive!\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSeasonal summer salads, here we are! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1732\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1732w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-728x925.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-768x975.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-1209x1536.jpg 1209w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-1612x2048.jpg 1612w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-150x191.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1732px) 100vw, 1732px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201732%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1732w, https://www.howsweeteats.c