berry-salad-3-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1699px) 100vw, 1699px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201699%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-scaled.jpg 1699w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-768x994.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-1186x1536.jpg 1186w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-1582x2048.jpg 1582w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-3-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s sure to be the salad of the summer. Festive, delicious and satisfying. Plus perfect for a big BBQ! Great for Memorial Day weekend, the 4th of July or any summer weeknight you want something fresh and wonderful. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI LOVE salads just like this. I’ve shared \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2020/07/triple-berry-salad/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ea triple berry crunch salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e before that has roasted chickpeas. And in \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/43zmAGA\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEasy Everyday\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, I have another really delish berry arugula salad! The combination of the peppery arugula against the sweet berries is perfect and one we adore. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1805\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-scaled.jpg 1805w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-728x887.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-768x936.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-1260x1536.jpg 1260w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-1680x2048.jpg 1680w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-150x183.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1805px) 100vw, 1805px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201805%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-scaled.jpg 1805w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-728x887.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-768x936.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-1260x1536.jpg 1260w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-1680x2048.jpg 1680w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-150x183.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd I even love making an easy salad like this as a starter for dinner. If there are berries involved, I can usually get my kids on board! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis salad has so much more than just berries though. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1686\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-150x196.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1686px) 100vw, 1686px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201686%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1686w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-728x950.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-768x1002.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-1177x1536.jpg 1177w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-1569x2048.jpg 1569w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-150x196.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThese pistachios clusters… oh my gosh. I want to eat these forever. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThey are inspired by the pepitas in \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2017/09/fall-kale-salad-harvest-honeycrisp-apple/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003emy harvest honeycrisp salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. But I skipped the spices, made them in a skillet instead of the oven and they are so simple.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd SO crunchy! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI mean, I could easily snack on these alone. But in a salad? Holy cow. They elevate it so much. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1715\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1715w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-728x934.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-768x985.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-1197x1536.jpg 1197w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-1596x2048.jpg 1596w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201715%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-scaled.jpg 1715w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-728x934.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-768x985.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-1197x1536.jpg 1197w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-1596x2048.jpg 1596w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-150x192.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-7-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAnd let’s talk about the dressing!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI have two similar dressings – my blue cheese vinaigrette and my smashed feta vinaigrette. This is like that, but with goat cheese. It is the best mix of creamy versus vinegar-based, because as the goat cheese warms up, it makes the dressing slightly creamy. But it’s not super thick and heavy, like a traditional creamy dressing.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-99179\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1662\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1662w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-728x964.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-768x1017.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-1160x1536.jpg 1160w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-1547x2048.jpg 1547w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-150x199.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1662px) 100vw, 1662px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201662%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-scaled.jpg 1662w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-728x964.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-768x1017.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-1160x1536.jpg 1160w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-1547x2048.jpg 1547w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-150x199.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-6-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI LOVE IT. The base uses red wine vinegar and lemon juice, a touch of lemon zest and crumbled goat cheese. It’s creamy and tangy in the best way possible and complements the berries so well. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt’s also delish when soaked up with some sourdough… just saying. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1713\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-scaled.jpg 1713w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-728x935.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-768x986.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-1196x1536.jpg 1196w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-1595x2048.jpg 1595w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-150x193.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1713px) 100vw, 1713px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201713%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-scaled.jpg 1713w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-728x935.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-768x986.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-1196x1536.jpg 1196w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-10-1595x2048.jpg 1595w, https: