8.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-12-768x905.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-12-1303x1536.jpg 1303w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-12-1737x2048.jpg 1737w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-12-150x177.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-12-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eBerry Arugula Salad with Pistachio Clusters\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-99195\" data-recipe-id=\"99195\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-8-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eRed, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99195\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 6\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis berry arugula salad is perfect for the summer! Topped with honey pistachio clusters and goat cheese vinaigrette, it\u0026#39;s simple, delicious, satisfying an super festive!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99195\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/salted-butter-1lb-good-gather-8482/-/A-54445965?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebutter\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eroasted, salted pistachios\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2 to 3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-clover-honey-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54436198?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ehoney\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6 to 8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebaby arugula greens\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esliced strawberries\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-blueberries-6oz/-/A-85762477?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eblueberries\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eblack berries\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ered raspberries\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecrumbled goat cheese,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor topping\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003egoat cheese vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pompeian-red-wine-vinegar-16-fl-oz/-/A-47846730?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ered wine vinegar\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/lemon-each/-/A-15013629?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efresh lemon juice\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"13\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic clove,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"14\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"15\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-clover-honey-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-54436198?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ehoney\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"16\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/dijon-mustard-12oz-market-pantry-8482/-/A-14766261?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003edijon mustard\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"17\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"18\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"19\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3 to 4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecrumbled goat cheese\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99195\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003esalad\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99195-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eMake the pistachios first. Melt the butter in a skillet over medium heat. Add the pistachios and stir. Add in the honey and toss well. Cook the mixture until it’s simmering for 2 to 3 minutes. Pour the mixture onto a sheet of parchment paper and let it cool.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99195-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eToss the arugula with a pinch of salt and pepper. Add in the berries and toss. Make the dressing.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99195-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTake the pistachio clusters and coarsely chop them up. Sprinkle them all over the salad. Sprinkle on more goat cheese if you wish. Drizzle with the dressing and serve!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003egoat cheese vinaigrette\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99195-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhisk together all ingredients except the olive oil and goat cheese. Stream in the olive oil while whisking until emulsified. Stir in the goat cheese. The more you stir or shake, the creamier the dressing will get. This stays good in the fridge for 1 to 2 days.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSalad, Side Dish\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"red white and berry arugula salad\" width=\"1607\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/berry-arugula-salad/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Red, White and Berry Salad with Pistachio Clusters.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-scaled.jpg 1607w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-728x996.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-768x1051.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-1122x1536.jpg 1122w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-1496x2048.jpg 1496w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/red-white-berry-salad-15-150x205.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-widt